name: D0llywood1
description: '''Kimberly Sommers''' (born December 2, 2003), known professionally as '''D0llywood1''' (stylized in [[lowercase]]), is an American rapper, record producer and singer from [[Louisiana]] who gained virality online in the digicore scene. She would release her second mixtape ''This Is Just a Dream (and Soon I Will Awake)'' (2024), and later co-headline an American tour with [[Jane Remover]].
